            {
                "label": "a",
                "content": [
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "text": "The diagram shows the curve with equation \\(y = \\frac{1}{\\sqrt{x}} \\mathrm{e}^{\\sqrt{x}}\\) for \\(x \\geqslant 1\\) , together with a set of \\(n - 1\\) rectangles of unit width.",
                        "bbox": [
                            117,
                            515,
                            916,
                            553
                        ]
                    },
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "text": "(a) By considering the sum of the areas of these rectangles, show that",
                        "bbox": [
                            117,
                            566,
                            671,
                            585
                        ]
                    },
                    {
                        "type": "blockMath",
                        "blockMath": "\\[\\sum_{r = 1}^{n}\\frac{1}{\\sqrt{r}}\\mathrm{e}^{\\sqrt{r}}< \\left(2 + \\frac{1}{\\sqrt{n}}\\right)\\mathrm{e}^{\\sqrt{n}} - 2\\mathrm{e}. \\quad (5)\\]",
                        "bbox": [
                            370,
                            600,
                            914,
                            644
                        ]
                    }
                ]
            },
            {
                "label": "b",
                "content": [
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "text": "(b) Use a similar method to find, in terms of \\(n\\), a lower bound for \\(\\sum_{r=1}^{n} \\frac{1}{\\sqrt{r}} e^{\\sqrt{r}}\\). [4]",
                        "bbox": [
                            111,
