                "content": [
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "text": "6 (a) Starting from the definitions of tanh and sech in terms of exponentials, prove that",
                        "bbox": [
                            78,
                            71,
                            790,
                            88
                        ]
                    },
                    {
                        "type": "blockMath",
                        "blockMath": "\\[1 - \\tanh^2 u = \\text{sech}^2 u. \\quad [3]\\]",
                        "bbox": [
                            413,
                            99,
                            916,
                            120
                        ]
                    }
                ]
            },
            {
                "label": "b",
                "content": [
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "text": "(b) Show that \\(\\frac{d}{dt}(\\text{sech}^{-1}t) = -\\frac{1}{t\\sqrt{1-t^2}}\\). \\quad [4]",
                        "bbox": [
                            156,
                            512,
                            916,
                            550
                        ]
                    }
                ]
            },
            {
                "label": "c",
                "content": [
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "text": "It is given that",
                        "bbox": [
                            117,
                            72,
                            234,
                            88
                        ]
                    },
                    {
                        "type": "blockMath",
                        "blockMath": "\\[x = \\tanh^{-1} t \\quad \\text{and} \\quad y = t \\sech^{-1} t, \\quad \\text{for } 0 < t < 1.\\]",
                        "bbox": [
                            281,
                            100,
                            712,
                            120
                        ]
                    },
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "text": "(c) Show that \\(\\frac{dy}{dx} = -\\sqrt{1 - t^2} + (1 - t^2) \\sech^{-1} t\\).",
                        "bbox": [
                            117,
                            142,
                            489,
                            172
                        ]
                    }
                ]
            },
            {
                "label": "d",
                "content": [
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "text": "(d) Find \\(\\frac{d^2 y}{dx^2}\\) in terms of \\(t\\).",
                        "bbox": [
                            117,
                            456,
                            336,
                            486
                        ]
                    }
